data.text: Anyone else rockin’ a JLo perfume with me??

Ok ya’ll.. embracing my inner @JLo this season on @dancingabc didn’t stop at my fabulous, custom @versace scarves dress, oh no. I had my own JLo Glow perfume on deck! This wasn’t a prop either, I’ve been wearing this scent since she dropped it back in the day - it’s that good! 🙌🏽 https://t.co/3colxcWuGf

This first dress from finale night had me feelin’ like I was about to float away like a cloud (and trip on the stairs!!!) Already can’t wait until next season where you know we will take it up 10 notches. Cuz that’s how we do.💙
First Monday without my @dancingabc fam and I’m already missing all the dance, the glitz and the glam, and getting to play dress up each and every week! https://t.co/cdF4Bkx828

Mentor, friend, visionary, embracer of weirdness & oh so much fun. You didn’t see the world how it was, but how U wanted it to be. Tony Hsieh, thank You for being a teacher to us all. Your innovative spirit, ideas & plans will continue to thrive. Rest in HAPPINESS. 💛 https://t.co/IAN301CEdc

This pic screams...I woke up like this ✨ and by this I mean in a food coma. Who feels me?? Don’t mind if I stay in bed and do some online shopping then hit up some of those leftovers later. Lemme know what you’re shopping for or diggin into today! https://t.co/1eSTfB6Xcx

Happy Thanksgiving from my family to yours! I’m extra grateful for my mama this year. She is definitely #momgoals. Share your thanks for your mama, family, friends and kids in the replies. I wanna know who is important to you. 💛 https://t.co/7XsixJtRrv

Congrats to these two winners of the #MirrorBall 🏆. @kaitlynbristowe & @artemchigvintse so proud of you. 
#DWTS https://t.co/NB3Zi6QMD0
Sneaking up on you with those sneakers under my couture baby blue dress. 🤫 @DancingABC finale is LIVE on east coast now!!! 👟
And that goes for YOU, too. Whether you’re attacking a new hobby or dance move, keep on going! It’s the dedication that counts more than anything!💛

Tomorrow, it's the finale of @dancingabc, and a mirror ball winner will be CROWNED. The stars will showcase their intense moves taught by their pros. Some may hit them all on point, some may mess up, but the most important thing is to keep going, even if they forget a little.

Flash forward to showtime... I forgot ALL the darn moves! Feet all over the place, arms not knowing what the heck to do, a mess! 😂 I kept my focus though. I attacked the moves with the intensity the choreographer taught me, but to my own crazy drum.
For this runway, I studied and practiced with a choreographer that specialized in flamenco. I lived and breathed those moves. I knew them backwards and forwards. I was set! 💃🏽 https://t.co/osvIrY8G66

Entrepreneurship is NO joke. But, If you start with what you love.. Every day that you wake up will not feel like work. 

My passion? Ice cream. Go follow @smizecream to follow our journey as my team and I work tirelessly to bring the most super-premium ice cream to your palette! https://t.co/QhRlQM8q2M

Happy Saturday, y’all!! I don’t know about you, but I am ready for the weekend! I’ve been hard at work whipping up some AMAZING and UNIQUE flavors for @smizecream and I am loving sharing this entrepreneurial journey with you! 🍬🍫🍪🍰 https://t.co/1mCaZ5DzNy
Show ‘em some love in the comments, and let me know who you want to see win that 2020 mirror ball!💃🏽🕺🏽

Join me in applauding them and sending them some super luck for their final dances. ⁠⠀
⁠⠀
It all comes down to the FINALE this Monday, where there can only be ONE winner! Who will it be? @Nelly_Mo, @kaitlynbristowe, @NevSchulman, or @JustinaMachado?

These stars' journeys have been intense! It’s not easy and takes courage to put yourself out there every week, especially when it's something you're not used to doing. To show up on that dance floor and say “This is Me!”.

I’ve hosted TV for decades but it was my first time hosting this. It was also a new experience for the team to bring joy to homes across the country during such worldwide challenging times. But through it all, the crew came together to create such an amazing season!
Let's hear it for our stars heading to the FINALS! 🎉 It's been such a new experience for everyone this season on @dancingabc. https://t.co/z5UlBoUKum

How incredible are these dancers @BrittBStewart and @Dance10Alan??💛 We're going to miss them in the competition next week, but can't wait to see all of the amazing work they create next! Leave some love in the comments for these two, the @dancingabc fam sure does love them! https://t.co/xDEH4v6ZAI
THIS week, SEMI-FINALS! 🌟 Only 6 couples remain, freestyle dances and a double elimination - then next stop - FINALS! Let me know in the comments which star you want to win!

@BrunoTonioli made an ICONIC George Michael, @derekhough slayed his David Bowie look, and @carrieanninaba rocked some glam rocker chic I swore was Mariah Carey vibes! Fellow judges fun to the max even from 6 feet apart! 💛 https://t.co/CR8Ae9iqyw
🎶 Don’t be fooled by the #Barbz from the block... 😉. Had so much fun embracing my inner queens @NickiMinaj and @JLo on @DancingABC. https://t.co/6fWpEHuVuP

Quick reminder: crying isn’t weak. I love me some holiday season, but sometimes I need a good cry! Just because its “the most wonderful time of the year” doesn’t mean we can’t embrace our emotions (good & bad!) This has been a super hard year. Let it out. It’s a sign of strength. https://t.co/G6aCoEZCEL
Thanks to @supermodels_official on IG for finding these gems! 💎 #FlashbackFriday #FBF https://t.co/Mw1e3UGJUY

How about a little #90svibes to bring some fashion inspo to your feed? ✨ Here's just a few of my favorite looks from the archives, love that most of these looks would still be in today. Which one is your favorite? Lemme know in the comments! 💛 https://t.co/QFvp9coJ8n
As a family that has veterans, we send so much love and appreciation to other families that also have members that have served. #VeteransDay 💛

It’s officially holiday season which means… DESSERT! I love seeing the what everyone’s making for friends and family! I’m gonna see what typa situation I can make like this using some of our home kitchen test batches of @smizecream!

📷: @whataleats https://t.co/3IpRnjLy9U
Tonight, I’ll be rockin’ GREEN again, paying inspirational homage to an acting & music ICON. Who do you think I’ll be dressed like tonight? 🎶 And my 2nd outfit will be…..??!!!

But on to tonight! It is ICONS night, baby! Hip-Hop, Rock, Pop & R&B icons! The stars and pros will be inspired by their fave musical acts from head to toe and will be rocking out to famous jams. 🔥🔥🔥⁠

It was super emotional on @dancingabc last week, whew….😢 but we’re looking ahead! @brendnalexander put me in my favorite color last week, yellow! Plus a fab electric green gown.⁠ https://t.co/DyinXDlLo2
💛 https://t.co/z2dAfgMSrH

Feeling so encouraged by the incredible turnout of elections across the nation, especially the many women, BIPOC and LGBTQ+ people being elected to congress! Our voice.

The impact Stacey is making without even holding an official office is SO amazing and I commend her. Registering ~800,000 new voters in the state of Georgia!! That is HUGE! I love me some Atlanta, Georgia (I filmed LifeSize 2 there and my bestie from high school lives there!)

This powerful woman right here, @staceyabrams, has me INSPIRED. ⁠⠀
